data.description: WOW! What more can you ask for? The property backs up to the Core of Engineer, Walking distance to Lynn Creek Park, Joe Pool Lake & restaurant on the water! Close to other restaurants, hospitals, shopping, Hwy 360, 20W, Hwy 30, & nearby schools. Community offers a pool, playground, catch & release pond, with friendly ducks! This beautiful 2 story 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath, 2 living, gas fireplace, 2 dining, master bedroom downstairs with garden tub, walk in closet, standing shower, double vanities, & Kitchen has gas cooking with a range that is less than a year. C-fans in rms. Solar screens & partial view of the pond. Home has an open concept that is great for family gathering with a smooth flow throughout the bottom floor. The home faces North. HVAC inside & out for down stairs 8 mos., Water heater, 3 yrs, 5 year roof.  DFW 45 minutes or less. Centrally located between Dallas & Fort Worth. Owners are downsizing & have had great memories & it is time for the next family!
